<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 02 at 4:23AM EST  by NWS Burlington</headline>
<description>...Areas of a Wintry Mix Likely This Morning...
Where temperatures have remained below freezing overnight, a
wintry mix of light snow and freezing drizzle is likely to
produce hazardous driving conditions this morning. A light glaze
of snow and ice may quickly coat roadways, and untreated surfaces
will become extremely slippery and offer little or no traction.
Please use extreme caution, especially on bridges, overpasses, and
around curves. Allow plenty of stopping distance and avoid
braking suddenly.</description>
